title: Aha Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, German, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Serves hearty warming stews, including a vegan chili and vegan Greek potato stew, plus other dishes such as vegetable lasagna and risotto. Large selection of herbal teas and coffees. Mainly vegetarian food, with a few vegan options, one or two dishes contain meat. Vegan dishes clearly labelled. Warm, relaxed atmosphere. Previously named Laden Cafe.
